-4fbb-8b70-802934b24037/94f94f20-19bf-11f0-84b6-3da9fe0b3bef/file-jaoe38c1m9i3m043.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2025 (Online) 7th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 24 English\"></p>\n<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below:</p>","options":["B & E Only\n","B, C & D Only\n","A, C & D Only\n","B & D Only"],"correctOption":3,"solution":"<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m9p3dbl1/d20d9bfc-36bc-4428-8c12-10ccd2f6f6cc/20195150-1d98-11f0-862a-09b5d9ec6f0c/file-jaoe38c1m9p3dbl2.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m9p3dbl1/d20d9bfc-36bc-4428-8c12-10ccd2f6f6cc/20195150-1d98-11f0-862a-09b5d9ec6f0c/file-jaoe38c1m9p3dbl2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2025 (Online) 7th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 24 English Explanation\"></p>\n<p>Option (B) and (D) reaction are not able to form alkene as a product.</p>","marks":4,"negativeMarks":-1,"topic":"Hydrocarbon"},{"id":"1l5bdhm42","questionNumber":10,"subject":"Chemistry","section":"A","questionType":"MCQ","questionText":"<p>Which of the following reagents / reactions will convert 'A' to 'B' ?</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l5cm96yp/9a75fa00-3646-4f09-8991-de5041c3bca2/2325ff10-fed3-11ec-8624-ff35f7fd77e0/file-1l5cm96yq.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l5cm96yp/9a75fa00-3646-4f09-8991-de5041c3bca2/2325ff10-fed3-11ec-8624-ff35f7fd77e0/file-1l5cm96yq.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2022 (Online) 24th June Evening Shift Chemistry - Hydrocarbons Question 85 English\"></p>","options":["PCC oxidation","Oz